WEBVTT

00:06.758 --> 00:10.595
Well, another fine mess
you've gotten me into.

00:10.804 --> 00:13.890
How would I know she had knockout gas
in her make-up compact?

00:14.099 --> 00:18.770
I don't know, maybe because you've
fought her, like, two dozen times?

00:18.979 --> 00:20.939
[GROWLING AND SNARLING]

00:21.356 --> 00:23.149
CATWOMAN:
Looks like you're about to catch...

00:23.358 --> 00:26.653
...a very bad case
of cat-scratch fever, Batman.

00:30.782 --> 00:32.617
You're the one who's caught,
Catwoman...

00:32.826 --> 00:34.577
...in the crooked claws of crime.

00:34.786 --> 00:37.414
Spare me your morality, hero.

00:37.622 --> 00:41.668
Who deserves these precious symbols
of feline superiority more than I?

00:41.876 --> 00:47.298
Surely not the curators of that
musty old museum I rescued them from.

00:47.841 --> 00:51.136
Okay, Bats, what's it gonna be?
Bat-catnip to distract the kitties...

00:51.344 --> 00:54.264
...or a high-frequency Bat-a-ma-jig
to scramble their brains, huh?

00:54.472 --> 00:57.142
You've let larceny taint your loveliness,
Catwoman.

00:57.392 --> 01:00.603
My pets will soon silence
that insolent tongue of--

01:00.812 --> 01:02.856
Did you say lovely?

01:04.024 --> 01:08.153
Less talk, more utility belt, huh?
Are you even listening to me?

01:08.361 --> 01:10.947
Lovely, yes, but evil too.

01:11.156 --> 01:13.074
Give up this life of crime, Catwoman.

01:13.324 --> 01:15.952
Allow me to help rehabilitate you.

01:18.747 --> 01:21.124
Wait. Are you two flirting?

01:21.332 --> 01:25.128
Oh, always trying to declaw me,
Batman...

01:25.336 --> 01:29.632
...which is why I must clip your wings,
permanently.

01:29.841 --> 01:32.510
Not if I collar you first.

01:33.053 --> 01:36.848
You are. You're flirting. Flirterers!

01:38.933 --> 01:40.518
[GREEN ARROW SHOUTS]

01:40.727 --> 01:42.729
I told you we should have
taken his belt away.

01:42.937 --> 01:44.022
[HISSES]

01:44.230 --> 01:48.359
You two take the overgrown elf.
I'll take the Batman.

01:50.195 --> 01:51.738
[GRUNTING AND SHOUTING]

01:51.988 --> 01:53.782
Bats!

02:09.339 --> 02:12.092
You chose the wrong career, Batman.

02:12.342 --> 02:14.344
We could be partners in crime.

02:14.552 --> 02:16.596
The perfect power couple.

02:16.846 --> 02:18.431
I'm a servant of justice.

02:23.645 --> 02:26.439
But justice is always
looking for new recruits.

02:28.650 --> 02:29.776
Can you believe those two?

02:30.026 --> 02:31.444
[LAUGHS THEN GAGS]

02:31.694 --> 02:34.114
Shut your cat box, pal.

02:35.949 --> 02:39.119
Time for these kittens to get back
to the museum where they belong.

02:39.327 --> 02:42.205
They belong with the one
who would appreciate them most.

02:42.413 --> 02:46.918
What can I say?
I'm a girl with a taste for only the finest.

02:47.627 --> 02:49.420
Oh, give me a break.

02:49.629 --> 02:53.424
Ease up, Arrow. She's only a cat burglar,
not a violent psychopath.

02:53.633 --> 02:56.553
Are you forgetting she nearly
turned us into cat food back there?

02:56.761 --> 02:59.389
[CATWOMAN SHOUTS
AND GREEN ARROW GRUNTS]

03:00.306 --> 03:03.393
- You have so got the hots for her.
- Nonsense.

03:03.601 --> 03:06.104
My only interest in her is rehabilitation.

03:06.688 --> 03:10.233
So letting her escape
is part of your reform therapy?

03:10.441 --> 03:12.986
I'm gonna have to try that one
on Clock King next time.

03:13.194 --> 03:16.531
Don't worry, I have a hunch
I'll know where to find her soon.

04:06.289 --> 04:07.665
[GRUNTS]

04:15.506 --> 04:20.178
The children and I
have been waiting for you, Batman.

04:23.097 --> 04:27.477
Psycho Pirate. When the Outsiders went
missing I suspected you were behind it.

04:27.685 --> 04:30.772
But this is sick, even for you.

04:31.356 --> 04:35.693
All I'm doing is giving the little ones
a much deserved nap.

04:35.902 --> 04:40.990
Can I help it if their nightmares
taste so delectable?

04:41.241 --> 04:44.786
You're nothing but a psychic vampire
who preys on the emotions of others...

04:45.036 --> 04:46.913
...but it ends now.

04:49.916 --> 04:51.000
Uh-uh-uh-uh.

04:51.251 --> 04:53.711
Opening those chambers
while the program is running...

04:53.962 --> 04:57.257
...will fry their tiny brains.

04:57.465 --> 05:01.177
And pull me out and no one wakes up.

05:01.844 --> 05:03.596
They're only kids, Pirate.

05:03.846 --> 05:06.099
What will it take
to make you release them?

05:06.432 --> 05:07.684
[LAUGHING]

05:07.892 --> 05:12.522
I'll stop when I've picked
their minds clean.

05:14.649 --> 05:19.862
Then I'm coming in
to show you what a real nightmare is.

05:20.113 --> 05:24.117
Just remember, Batman,
when you die in the dream world...

05:24.325 --> 05:25.994
...you never wake up.

05:26.202 --> 05:29.247
[PSYCHO PIRATE LAUGHING]

05:38.589 --> 05:40.591
[GIRL SOBBING]

05:44.178 --> 05:46.306
KATANA:
I'm so sorry, Master Takahiro...

05:46.556 --> 05:48.808
...I never should have
opened my big mouth.

05:49.017 --> 05:53.062
Now Takeo knows the sword is here
and he's coming for it.

05:54.397 --> 05:58.067
Shh, young one,
I will deal with Takeo...

05:58.318 --> 06:01.070
...but you must find a place to hide.

06:16.169 --> 06:19.088
I've come for the katana sword,
Takahiro.

06:26.137 --> 06:30.350
He's going to kill Master Takahiro,
and it's my fault.

06:30.558 --> 06:33.686
Katana, listen to me,
this is only a dream.

06:33.895 --> 06:35.938
Psycho Pirate is manipulating you.

06:36.147 --> 06:38.608
No. It's all my fault.

06:39.901 --> 06:41.277
At last.

06:47.033 --> 06:49.202
It will do you no good.

06:49.410 --> 06:55.500
Only a warrior of pure mind
and gentle heart may wield it.

06:56.042 --> 06:58.795
Wishful thinking from an old fool.

06:59.003 --> 07:03.007
A shame you won't live to see
how wrong you are.

07:18.272 --> 07:19.649
[GASPS]

07:27.115 --> 07:29.534
You're seeing something
that happened years ago.

07:29.742 --> 07:32.578
It's a nightmare.
There's nothing we can do now.

07:33.287 --> 07:37.250
I know. I've relived this nightmare
a hundred times.

07:37.458 --> 07:40.211
But this time, I'm getting revenge.

07:40.962 --> 07:43.214
Wait. Katana. No!

07:43.589 --> 07:45.341
[GROANING]

07:45.550 --> 07:47.427
KATANA:
Takeo!

07:47.677 --> 07:49.262
[KATANA SHOUTS
AND KATEO GRUNTS]

07:57.562 --> 07:59.605
[GROANING]

08:12.952 --> 08:14.954
[GRUNTING AND SHOUTING]

08:17.290 --> 08:18.791
[LAUGHING]

08:20.960 --> 08:22.920
You killed him, my clear.

08:23.463 --> 08:26.090
You and that mouth
you can't keep shut.

08:39.103 --> 08:42.106
Go on, Katana, take your revenge.

08:45.401 --> 08:46.736
Strike me down!

08:50.781 --> 08:54.035
This isn't our way.
It's not Takahiro's way.

09:02.793 --> 09:05.463
Is that why you don't talk anymore,
Katana?

09:05.713 --> 09:10.009
Because your big mouth
betrayed Takahiro?

09:15.681 --> 09:17.308
You know he's wrong.

09:17.517 --> 09:19.810
Your silence is in honor of Takahiro.

09:20.019 --> 09:21.145
You didn't betray him.

09:21.354 --> 09:24.982
Takahiro sacrificed himself
to make you reach your full potential.

09:25.191 --> 09:31.030
He knew only the warrior of pure mind
and gentle heart could wield that sword.

09:36.118 --> 09:38.579
And I've forgotten
his most important lesson...

09:39.747 --> 09:42.041
---self-control-.

09:50.424 --> 09:54.554
PSYCHO PIRATE: The girl's guilt
was quite tasty while it lasted...

09:55.096 --> 09:57.807
...but I'm still hungry.

10:00.142 --> 10:03.229
He feeds off rage.
You were just the appetizer.

10:03.437 --> 10:06.524
It looks like Black Lightning
is the main course.

10:22.748 --> 10:25.293
Black Lightning
has always been a ball of fury.

10:25.543 --> 10:28.004
I can only imagine
what horrors he's reliving.

10:32.383 --> 10:33.342
[GIRL SCREAMS]

10:33.551 --> 10:37.013
Better brace ourselves.
This could be deeply disturbing.

10:37.221 --> 10:39.307
[CROWD SHOUTING]

10:58.451 --> 11:01.037
Sprinkles? On coffee?

11:01.579 --> 11:03.539
What are you, a 6 year old?

11:12.757 --> 11:16.844
Oh, so you're the reason I had to throw
away a brand-new pair of high-tops...

11:17.053 --> 11:19.722
...Mr. I-Forgot-the-Scoop-at-Home.

11:20.264 --> 11:21.891
[nos YELPING]

11:22.099 --> 11:23.726
And, lady, didn't you get the memo?

11:23.934 --> 11:26.228
No white after Labor Day!

11:29.940 --> 11:33.986
Not exactly the deep core
of emotional trauma I expected.

11:36.530 --> 11:38.574
[HORN HONKING]

11:41.160 --> 11:45.081
You drive a vehicle that big
just to haul a bag of groceries?

11:48.959 --> 11:50.211
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

11:51.420 --> 11:55.091
Black Lightning, you need to relax
and get ahold of yourself.

11:55.299 --> 11:58.594
Relax? How can I relax
when I know something like that...

11:58.803 --> 12:02.431
...is coming to a theater near me?

12:04.141 --> 12:05.810
That won't solve anything.

12:06.060 --> 12:10.106
You're right.
I have to go after the filmmakers.

12:10.314 --> 12:13.109
You're a superhero.
You're bigger than this.

12:13.317 --> 12:17.029
You know what else makes me angry?
Superheroes wearing capes.

12:19.407 --> 12:20.783
You can't even fly!

12:21.701 --> 12:23.953
No, honey, I was going to--

12:24.161 --> 12:27.248
No, you were supposed to
pick up the kids.

12:27.456 --> 12:30.793
Hey, cyborg,
your call is about to drop.

12:33.504 --> 12:35.089
[GROANING]

12:43.097 --> 12:47.685
Seen your old master around lately,
chatterbox?

12:49.687 --> 12:51.522
[LAUGHING]

13:03.534 --> 13:05.578
BLACK LIGHTNING:
So, what's with the bat decal?

13:05.786 --> 13:07.747
You're like a walking bull's-eye.

13:13.043 --> 13:15.129
[LAUGHING]

13:16.505 --> 13:19.800
MAN:
Hiya, kids. Who needs a hug today?

13:20.009 --> 13:21.635
Oh, no. It can't be!

13:21.844 --> 13:23.220
[DREAM-LIKE MUSIC PLAYING ON TV]

13:23.429 --> 13:24.555
Not that!

13:24.764 --> 13:27.224
Not Yorick, the Unicorn!

13:27.433 --> 13:29.310
[LAUGHING]

13:31.437 --> 13:33.898
It's only a kids' TV show.

13:34.106 --> 13:36.650
Hugs do not solve
everybody's problems!

13:36.859 --> 13:38.152
Neither does rage.

13:38.360 --> 13:41.655
Every time you use your lightning,
Psycho Pirate gets stronger.

13:51.457 --> 13:54.543
Every day is free hug day.

13:55.085 --> 13:57.254
The heck it is.

13:59.882 --> 14:03.427
ALL:
Rainbows are made of unicorn smiles.

14:03.677 --> 14:07.681
Bath time is playtime
and good, clean fun.

14:07.973 --> 14:09.016
[GASPS]

14:09.225 --> 14:11.519
ALL:
Rainbows are made of unicorn smiles.

14:11.727 --> 14:14.688
Happiness is a warm hug.

14:14.897 --> 14:16.941
That warm enough for you?

14:17.566 --> 14:20.027
You're showing the same
resentment and intolerance...

14:20.236 --> 14:23.364
...that drove the Outsiders underground
in the first place.

14:23.572 --> 14:27.952
Use your passion
to stop the real threat: Psycho Pirate.

14:33.123 --> 14:35.209
[BLACK LIGHTNING GROANING]

14:38.087 --> 14:41.715
- He's right. Okay, okay.
ALL: Rainbows are made of smiles.

14:41.966 --> 14:44.051
It's only a silly children's show.

14:44.301 --> 14:50.432
- Happiness is a warm hug.
ALL: Rainbows are made of smiles.

14:54.019 --> 14:55.813
PSYCHO PIRATE:
Congratulations, Batman.

14:56.021 --> 14:59.733
You've snatched two succulent courses
from my jaws.

14:59.942 --> 15:03.445
But I still have room for dessert.

15:05.698 --> 15:07.324
Well, the worst is over.

15:07.533 --> 15:10.160
Once we spring Metamorpho,
we're home free, right?

15:10.369 --> 15:12.371
- Don't be so sure.
- You kidding?

15:12.580 --> 15:16.000
Happy-go-lucky Morpho? I've never
once seen him lose his temper.

15:20.462 --> 15:21.463
[GROWLS]

15:21.672 --> 15:24.008
Looks like you're about to.

15:44.695 --> 15:46.739
[CAR ALARM BLARING]

15:55.873 --> 15:57.917
[SHOUTING]

16:01.879 --> 16:05.799
This cannot be the same Metamorpho
who sleeps with a Fuzzy Furry Doll.

16:06.050 --> 16:10.179
Metamorpho's rage has been
Psycho Pirate's real fuel source all along.

16:10.429 --> 16:12.681
You two were just pawns
to keep me busy.

16:12.932 --> 16:15.059
Gee, thanks for that jolt of confidence,
Bats.

16:15.309 --> 16:17.728
[METAMORPHO
GROWLING AND SHOUTING]

16:24.985 --> 16:27.029
Okay, I get it, he's really steamed.

16:27.237 --> 16:29.281
But what about?

16:31.825 --> 16:33.619
Look at them.

16:33.827 --> 16:36.664
They know they can walk in public
without being stared at...

16:36.872 --> 16:40.376
...so they laugh at you
behind your back.

16:40.626 --> 16:43.253
They call you a freak.

16:50.177 --> 16:52.846
Wait a minute.
If this is all a dream world...

16:53.055 --> 16:55.057
...he can't really hurt us. Right?

16:55.265 --> 16:57.184
In Psycho Pirate's world he can...

16:57.393 --> 16:59.895
...but we have to make sure
not to hurt Metamorpho.

17:00.104 --> 17:01.605
He doesn't know what he's doing.

17:06.735 --> 17:09.196
We can't blast him?
Then what are we gonna do?

17:09.405 --> 17:12.032
- Reason with him?
- It's our only choice.

17:12.282 --> 17:14.576
His anger comes from
feeling he's an outcast.

17:14.785 --> 17:16.328
We have to remind him he's not.

17:18.455 --> 17:19.415
[SIGHS]

17:19.665 --> 17:21.917
Well, here goes nothing.

17:23.752 --> 17:25.546
Morpho, buddy...

17:25.754 --> 17:29.717
...how can you be so mad when you've
got the coolest powers in the world?

17:32.428 --> 17:34.847
Me, I'm just a talking electric socket...

17:35.055 --> 17:37.850
...and Katana,
she's a glorified paring knife.

17:38.058 --> 17:40.686
But we count on you, dude.

17:40.894 --> 17:44.773
You count on me?

17:45.441 --> 17:47.192
It's working.

17:47.443 --> 17:49.737
No, they use you.

17:49.945 --> 17:53.282
They're jealous of your power
and want it for themselves.

18:06.670 --> 18:10.716
We need a two-pronged attack. You keep
trying to get through to Metamorpho...

18:10.924 --> 18:12.968
...I'll take care of Psycho Pirate.

18:18.807 --> 18:20.601
You don't really hate us, do you?

18:25.981 --> 18:29.401
Okay. Not the answer I was hoping for.

18:37.868 --> 18:39.787
[GRUNTS]

18:42.998 --> 18:44.333
You're weak, Pirate.

18:44.541 --> 18:47.961
You don't have the guts to take on
the heavy hitters, so you go after kids.

18:48.170 --> 18:52.883
That's it, Batman. Feed me your fury.

19:02.226 --> 19:03.852
[BOTH GRUNTING]

19:10.109 --> 19:12.361
[GRUNTING AND SHOUTING]

19:15.322 --> 19:16.448
Metamorpho!

19:19.493 --> 19:22.621
We became the Outsiders
because we all felt we were different...

19:22.830 --> 19:25.707
...alone and unable to fit in
with everyone else.

19:25.916 --> 19:29.670
But that's what makes us, all of us,
so cool.

19:34.925 --> 19:36.135
We're a team.

19:36.343 --> 19:40.931
We all need each other,
and we need you.

19:55.445 --> 19:59.366
<i>AWÂ» Natty, guys. My bad.</i>

20:01.451 --> 20:04.663
"Sh. Hugs.

20:26.977 --> 20:28.562
[SHOUTING]

20:35.485 --> 20:36.904
No.

20:43.493 --> 20:47.080
You didn't. Even a psyche
as warped as yours could never--

20:47.289 --> 20:51.001
Of course I did,
they're of no use to me now.

20:51.210 --> 20:55.005
But remember,
you're the reason they became heroes...

20:55.214 --> 20:57.257
...so it's your fault they're--

20:57.466 --> 20:59.509
[SHOUTING]

21:02.054 --> 21:07.893
No greater anger
than the anger of the just.

21:11.939 --> 21:13.232
You're still feeding.

21:15.025 --> 21:16.944
This isn't the real lab.

21:17.152 --> 21:19.404
Indeed, Batman.

21:19.947 --> 21:25.577
We're in your nightmare now,
and there is no escape.

21:25.786 --> 21:27.579
[CACKLING]

21:27.788 --> 21:30.249
There's always an escape.

21:35.254 --> 21:37.047
What? What are you doing?

21:37.256 --> 21:40.717
I'm feeding you the one thing
you can't stomach...

21:40.926 --> 21:42.928
n-happy thoughts.

21:44.304 --> 21:48.141
I don't always need fury to fight with.

21:49.017 --> 21:50.936
You're looking thin, Pirate.

21:51.144 --> 21:54.147
You should really eat something.
Try this.

22:01.196 --> 22:03.240
[SCREAMING]

22:08.912 --> 22:12.040
I say we take this creep
out back and...

22:12.708 --> 22:17.421
Ahem, and let the, uh, authorities
deal with him.

22:18.839 --> 22:23.343
Speaking of authorities, keep an eye
on Psycho Pirate while I call them.

22:23.552 --> 22:26.221
Yo, those must have been
some majorly happy thoughts...

22:26.430 --> 22:28.473
...to turn that machine into a junk pile.

22:28.682 --> 22:32.978
Yeah.
What are Batman's happiest thoughts?
